        {
            "title": "川普暗示可能重新談判英國貿易協議,與施紀賢關係緊張",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IDlX4K35u5avRPuXCUSvjA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6M0QA_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國總統川普週三表示,他可能會重新考慮與英國達成的貿易協議條款,理由是對英國國內政策以及首相施紀賢存在分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在週三<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"發布\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:發布;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://x.com/Stone_SkyNews\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">發布</a>的Sky News採訪中告訴記者:「我們給了他們一個好的貿易協議。比我必須給的更好。這總是可以改變的。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普和施紀賢去年同意實施一項貿易協定,該協定降低了英國主要出口商品的關稅,並提高了英國對某些美國農產品的配額。與美國與其他盟友達成的協議相比,該協議被認為更為優惠。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-029f1ee8-5577-36ae-b362-17992b3e877e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這番言論正值兩國就英國不願參與美國對伊朗戰爭而發生爭執之際。川普告訴Sky News,在英國國王本月稍後訪問美國之前,與伊朗達成協議「非常有可能」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"表示\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:表示;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.sky.com/story/iran-war-latest-trump-us-israel-ceasefire-deal-strait-of-hormuz-blockade-strikes-oil-lebanon-13509565\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">表示</a>:「他們被打得很慘。這非常有可能。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據戰爭的最新進展,中央司令部週二表示,美國已全面實施對伊朗港口和航運的封鎖,這是在川普總統下令採取這一行動以向德黑蘭施壓促其停火的幾天後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當被問及美英關係狀況時,川普表示關係「曾經更好過」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普說:「關係如何?這種關係是:當我們向他們尋求幫助時,他們不在那裡。當我們需要他們時,他們不在那裡。當我們不需要他們時,他們也不在那裡。而且他們現在仍然不在那裡。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E8%88%87%E6%96%BD%E7%B4%80%E8%B3%A2%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-102209934.html",
